# Terraform runtime files
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform/*
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.*
**/tfplan
**/*.tfplan
**/crash.log
**/crash.*.log
**/.terraform.tfstate.lock.info

# Local variable files with real tenant, subscription, object IDs, or secrets
**/*.auto.tfvars
**/*.auto.tfvars.json
**/terraform.tfvars
**/terraform.tfvars.json
!**/*.tfvars.example

# Kubernetes and cloud credentials
**/kubeconfig
**/*.kubeconfig
**/.kube/
**/azureProfile.json
**/accessTokens.json

# Generated archives and temporary files
*.zip
*.tar
*.tar.gz
*.tmp
*.bak
*.backup

# OS/editor files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
.vscode/
.idea/

# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc

